name: viewer-mix_v1.7
description:
v1.7

该模型的制作借鉴了AOM3的合并方法。

并同步更新了针对此版本的负面嵌入，veryBadImageNegative_v1.3。

The production of this model draws on the merging method of AOM3.

And synchronously updated negative embeddings for this version,veryBadImageNegative_v1.3.

v1.3

改动：

1、 将vae文件烘焙进去了。

2、调整了原料的比例重新进行混合，优化了色调和氛围，使其看起来整体光影效果更具戏剧性。

3、训练了一个名为veryBadImageNegative的负面嵌入，所有的例子均使用了这个负面嵌入。

Changes:

1. Baked the vae file.

2. After adjusting the weight, re-mixing is performed to optimize the tone and atmosphere, making the overall light and shadow effect more dramatic.

3. A negative embedding called veryBadImageNegative is trained, and all examples use this negative embedding.

v1.0

该模型可以生成高质量的动漫风格壁纸、动漫风格角色、自然风景插图。

推荐使用pastel-waifu-diffusion.vae.pt，所有例子都是使用这个vae生成的。

this model can generate high-quality anime style wallpaper, anime style characters, and natural scenery illustrations.

pastel-waifu-diffusion.vae.pt is recommended, all examples are generated using this vae.
